column183: Note from the ICJ Registry: This file number (H-2785) refers to a folder that was submitted to the Court with the Nuremberg Trial Archives although the content might not properly be considered as an IMT record but rather belonging to the Allied Control Authority. The U.S. National Archives and Records Administration declassified the record group containing this document in 1977, and the document is publicly available there under file number 12004/3 “Clemency To Prisoners Serving Sentences”, https://catalog.archives.gov/id/1853700.
